column1: Memorial service will be held at 10:30 AM
column5: at Prince of Peace Lutheran Church with Rev. Joe Andrajack and Chaplin John Elser officiating. Janese graciously and unselfishly gave the gift of her body to be used for the advancement of medical science. Arrangements are by Schooler Funeral Home
column6: 4100 S. Georgia. The family will receive friends from 6 to 7 PM Friday
